{"title":"czq的原木收获","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":512,"tags":["2020小学期"],"operation":{"submit":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/problem/1239#submit_code","submissions":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/submissions?problem_id=1239","statistics":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/problem/1239/statistics/fastest","testdata":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/problem/1239/testdata","discussion":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/discussion/problem/1239"},"statement":[{"title":"题目描述","type":"description","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"冬天，czq的原木林场可以开始采伐。一共有$n$棵原木可以收获，分别的长度为$a_i$。\r\n\r\n原木能卖个好价钱，但必须切成长度为$m$的标准长度，$m$长度的原木能卖$m$元，其他长度的无法出售。\r\n\r\n但现在的问题是，工人们需要从czq的原木中锯下共$k$长度的木头燃烧用以取暖。\r\n\r\n葛朗台czq肉痛不已，他想知道在满足完取暖需求之后，他还能将原木最多卖出多少钱？"},{"title":"输入格式","type":"input_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"第一行三个整数$n,m,k$，含义如上。\r\n\r\n接下来一行$n$个整数，为原木的长度。"},{"title":"输出格式","type":"output_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"仅一个整数，为最多卖出的价钱。"},{"title":"样例","type":"example","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"### 样例输入\r\n```\r\n6 2 9\r\n1 1 4 5 1 4\r\n```\r\n\r\n### 样例输出\r\n```\r\n6\r\n```"},{"title":"数据范围与提示","type":"limit_and_hint","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"$1 \\leq n \\leq 10^5$\r\n\r\n$0 \\leq k \\leq \\sum\\limits_{i=1}^n a_i $\r\n\r\n$1 \\leq a_i,m \\leq 10^9$ "}]}